	<clause id="_what_constitutes_an_msdi" obligation="normative"><title>What constitutes an MSDI?</title><p id="_7d025a50-640e-408c-88d8-1eb1c24d2270">An MSDI can be described as a framework comprising the key components shown in <xref target="fig1"/>.</p>
	<figure id="fig1">
	<name>The Four pillars of MSDI</name>
